line = 1731 | 1 | task to do, and at the beginning it is to know. You can help me here.
line = 1732 | 1 | Can you tell me what went before your going to Transylvania? Later on I
line = 1733 | 1 | may ask more help, and of a different kind; but at first this will do."
line = 1734 | 1 | 
