line = 1738 | 1 | 
line = 1739 | 1 | "Then I am with you heart and soul. As you go by the 10:30 train, you
line = 1740 | 1 | will not have time to read them; but I shall get the bundle of papers.
line = 1741 | 1 | You can take them with you and read them in the train."
