line = 2127 | 1 | observant, and not sleepy enough to betray my trust so altogether I had
line = 2128 | 1 | a dreary, miserable time.
line = 2129 | 1 | 
line = 2130 | 1 | Suddenly, as I turned round, I thought I saw something like a white
line = 2131 | 1 | streak, moving between two dark yew-trees at the side of the churchyard
