line = 2149 | 1 | 
line = 2150 | 1 | "Yes, it is a child, but who brought it here? And is it wounded?" I
line = 2151 | 1 | asked.
line = 2152 | 1 | 
line = 2153 | 1 | "We shall see," said the Professor, and with one impulse we took our way
line = 2154 | 1 | out of the churchyard, he carrying the sleeping child.
line = 2155 | 1 | 
line = 2156 | 1 | When we had got some little distance away, we went into a clump of
line = 2157 | 1 | trees, and struck a match, and looked at the child's throat. It was
line = 2158 | 1 | without a scratch or scar of any kind.
line = 2159 | 1 | 
line = 2160 | 1 | "Was I right?" I asked triumphantly.
line = 2161 | 1 | 
line = 2162 | 1 | "We were just in time," said the Professor thankfully.
line = 2163 | 1 | 
line = 2164 | 1 | We had now to decide what we were to do with the child, and so consulted
line = 2165 | 1 | about it. If we were to take it to a police-station we should have to
line = 2166 | 1 | give some account of our movements during the night; at least, we should
line = 2167 | 1 | have had to make some statement as to how we had come to find the child.
line = 2168 | 1 | So finally we decided that we would take it to the Heath, and when we
line = 2169 | 1 | heard a policeman coming, would leave it where he could not fail to find
line = 2170 | 1 | it; we would then seek our way home as quickly as we could. All fell out
line = 2171 | 1 | well. At the edge of Hampstead Heath we heard a policeman's heavy
line = 2172 | 1 | tramp, and laying the child on the pathway, we waited and watched until
line = 2173 | 1 | he saw it as he flashed his lantern to and fro. We heard his exclamation
line = 2174 | 1 | of astonishment, and then we went away silently. By good chance we got a
line = 2175 | 1 | cab near the "Spaniards," and drove to town.
line = 2176 | 1 | 
line = 2177 | 1 | I cannot sleep, so I make this entry. But I must try to get a few hours'
line = 2178 | 1 | sleep, as Van Helsing is to call for me at noon. He insists that I shall
line = 2179 | 1 | go with him on another expedition.
line = 2180 | 1 | 
line = 2181 | 1 |        *       *       *       *       *
