line = 2486 | 1 | the wide world will I consent to any mutilation of her dead body. Dr.
line = 2487 | 1 | Van Helsing, you try me too far. What have I done to you that you should
line = 2488 | 1 | torture me so? What did that poor, sweet girl do that you should want to
line = 2489 | 1 | cast such dishonour on her grave? Are you mad that speak such things, or
line = 2490 | 1 | am I mad to listen to them? Don't dare to think more of such a
